title: Origins Exclusive Worldwide Premiere.mp4
description:
This very well made documentary was released on 11/22/14 reviewing how humans used to eat and live in the past and compares it with how humans are living today in "Modern" society. 

THIS IS A MUST WATCH VIDEO FOR EVERYONE. I am a writer and producer who has studied this information on my own and I want you to know that this video is a CLASSIC documentary filled with true information that everyone must study in order to improve our health, food, and life style for ourselves and for humans all around the world

Please go to WELL.ORG for more information about this organization and to buy their DVD or at least make a donation like I did to help them keep producing videos revealing the truths of life
